{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I was also trained to take certain actions [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] under that station like that, which were unpredictable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So what I did at that time, they placed their guns-- they didn't have pistols.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They had long, long old-fashioned guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they placed them against the wall as they were reading and checking all these documents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I just had seconds to think what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "What I did, I kicked the guns as hard as I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They flew up in the air.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I started running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Get down on my knees, jump up, run across the street, confusing them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Well, it took them maybe 10 seconds to recover the guns, 15 seconds takes-- you know, 'til they pulled the guns and they start aiming.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Literally heard bullets flying by me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But now I ran into a busy street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were shooting, but they were reluctant to shoot at other people while they were aiming at me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I realized suddenly that there was what's called a transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Transport meant a group of Jews that are being deported somewheres, either into a camp or-- or being deported to the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I had no idea where they were being taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But there were Hungarian soldiers on both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there were like 50 to 75 Jews on the streets that were being walked somewheres.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So quickly on my hands and knees got up and started marching with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I literally marched by these two soldiers that were running around like mad looking for me to get me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But one thing, they never looked into this transport because, I mean, he's not in there, he's running away from us, while I'm marching by this building.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
